{"bangumi":{"date":"2024-01-06","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/22/ef/415772_fU77d.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/22/ef/415772_fU77d.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/22/ef/415772_fU77d.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/22/ef/415772_fU77d.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/22/ef/415772_fU77d.jpg"},"summary":"随处可见的普通学生佐藤春人，私底下暗恋着青梅竹马的野中姬乃。就在决定要告白的某天，佐藤突然被姬乃告知必须要搬往到遥远的地方。无法放弃恋心的佐藤追逐姬乃的脚步，冲进了光芒之中……。一睁开眼，抵达的地方居然是异世界！在还搞不清楚状况的他，在被姬乃一吻之下，便成为了众所期望的传说勇者－「戒王」，挺身面对世界的威胁。\r\n姬乃是位异世界当中只存在5位「戒指公主」的其中一人。此外，为了将戒指真正的力量发挥出来，必须和剩下的4位公主们结婚才行……！？\r\n与5位公主的异世界新婚奇幻大冒险，就此揭开序幕！","name":"結婚指輪物語","name_cn":"婚戒物语","tags":[{"name":"后宫","count":297,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2024年1月","count":236,"total_cont":0},{"name":"卖肉","count":231,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":191,"total_cont":0},{"name":"异世界","count":146,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":144,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":139,"total_cont":0},{"name":"StapleEntertainment","count":102,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":99,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2024","count":78,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":62,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":54,"total_cont":0},{"name":"穿越","count":43,"total_cont":0},{"name":"肉番","count":26,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2024年","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"佐藤元","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冒险","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"肉","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"厕纸","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"直谷隆","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"婚戒物语","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"直谷たかし","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2024冬","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"露点","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"季番","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"24冬","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2024.1","count":2,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"婚戒物语"},{"key":"